WEBVTT

1
00:00:07.266 --> 00:00:09.200
Bucheon, what are you doing here?

2
00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:11.600
Mom, I secretly sent someone to arrest the maid of the Zhang family and interrogate her

3
00:00:11.600 --> 00:00:12.966
That's how I got your message.

4
00:00:12.966 --> 00:00:14.000
Sorry I'm late.

5
00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:14.966
Are you all right?

6
00:00:15.933 --> 00:00:17.266
I don't mind.

7
00:00:17.700 --> 00:00:19.700
Take me back to find Xiaojie

8
00:00:20.266 --> 00:00:22.700
Even if I die, I want to be with Xiaojie

9
00:00:22.700 --> 00:00:24.500
Never be apart again

10
00:00:25.100 --> 00:00:26.466
Mom, don't worry

11
00:00:26.466 --> 00:00:28.566
I have a way to help you prove it. Go

12
00:00:32.100 --> 00:00:34.333
What? That bitch ran away?

13
00:00:34.333 --> 00:00:35.200
Oh, dear!

14
00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:36.700
Let me explain.

15
00:00:36.733 --> 00:00:39.466
He escaped while I was in the latrine

16
00:00:39.466 --> 00:00:41.000
We've been looking for this for days.

17
00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:42.800
There's no sign of him here

18
00:00:42.800 --> 00:00:44.566
I would have killed him long ago for a moment of regret

19
00:00:44.566 --> 00:00:46.200
You have to hug him and cause trouble for me

20
00:00:46.333 --> 00:00:47.633
Hurry up and find it for me

21
00:00:47.866 --> 00:00:50.300
If he comes back and talks nonsense in front of his wife

22
00:00:50.300 --> 00:00:51.466
Make madam believe

23
00:00:51.533 --> 00:00:52.866
What to do, don't think about it better for anyone

24
00:00:53.566 --> 00:00:54.600
These two beasts

25
00:00:54.600 --> 00:00:56.100
Success is not enough, failure requires life

26
00:00:56.200 --> 00:00:58.700
The old lady is not good, not good

27
00:00:59.400 --> 00:01:00.133
What's up?

28
00:01:00.133 --> 00:01:02.700
Madam, his investment failed and he owed a lot of debt

29
00:01:02.733 --> 00:01:04.333
Now the creditors are out there

30
00:01:04.333 --> 00:01:06.833
He also said that our Zhang family is about to go bankrupt

31
00:01:07.100 --> 00:01:08.400
Pardon me?

